Text.string: Whatcha gonna do, punch my ankles?
Knock the blonde right offa his skull!
Oh hey man! Sorry, gotta kill you.
Magic's just tech we don't yet understand!
You wanna scrap with the big kids?
They'll be back. They always come back.
Target lost. Kill bonus, definitely lost.
Yeah, I don't mind chilling for a while.
Where'd they go? It was just getting good!
Can't see my target. Can't see anything, really. These visors suck.
I'm full of holes over here!
Get over here and fix me up!
I paid my premium, where's the doc?
Medic! My suit's filling up with blood!
Wait, I can still fix this!
Why couldn't this have been YOU?!
Oh, now I'm REALLY gonna kill you!
This is fine! This is fine!
Tell my wife I was on fire!
Someone help me take this off!
Cold cold cold cold cold cold!
Why you gotta be like that?
Ah crap, I don't wanna be a snowman!
I regret strapping this generator to my body!
Somebody try punching it or something!
I didn't want to electrocute ME!
Ow! I thought-- ow! Hey, I-- OW!
Oh, for the love of ass!
My pack, it's out of control!
This is bad, this is really bad!
You were supposed to NOT do that!
This was NOT in the plan!
Aaah! It's eating through the shielding!
Getting' real bad over here, guys!
You better hope I don't get outta this!
It's eating through my shirt. My shiiirt!
What's that smell? Oh god, no!
Command, I've got a spill! I repeat-- argh!
I'm gonna leave a really cool skeleton!
Pack down! I repeat, pack down!
One more notch in the belt!
Have you seen my beach ball? I think it went over therrrrree...
“Look at me, I've got internal bleeding and a massive concussion!” [laughs]
This is YOU! This is what you look like! [laughs]
You! You call this competition?! [laughs] You're DONE!
You ain't nothin' but a bonus check to me! [laughs] Bam!
You... will never make it out of here alive! [laughs] Ugh!
Yeah! Hell yeah! Get some! Ugh!
Bring it, Vault Hunter! Bring it!
I was still soft... on the inside...
I died the way I lived... pissing and shitting.
Guess I won't get my bonus...
Thought I was too tough to die...
May flights of angels sing me... Digby Vermouth...
At least I died for a corporate cause...
Oh man, I just realized I'm a huge target.
I don't get paid enough for this!
This suit's great! I'm peeing! Right this second!
Guess I gotta work for it...
Uh... MAL? You won't believe this...
Now's a good time to be covered in sweet, sweet armor.
Does anyone have a comically large bone?
Rakks, ten o'clock! No, twelve! Aaah!
Gotta admit, I like your style!
That's gonna be fun to kill!
I'm gonna play with that when you're dead!
You're dead, and that thing's mine!
I'm paid by the kill, so thanks!
I'll kill that one fast, and that one slow!
I can do that too, I just don't wanna!
Yes, you're very special. Now die!
I'll get to you in a minute!
I can take you both on!
Get that garbage out of my FACE!
Aw, did you make that yourself?
I could use an extra shield too!
How long does that thing last?!
Don't make me come back there!
Got tricks up ALL your sleeves, huh?
I liked your other look better.
You a wrestler or something? Nice!
That's right! Fight for your life!
He was my friend, you ass!
He was two weeks from retirement!
When you kill one of us, you kill all of us! Wait...
We got more where he came from!
Throw it back! Throw it baaack!
I have a very cushy job, and you're ruining it!
Why don't you pick on someone twice your size?
At least TRY not to die!
Man, this was going better in my head.
Figures, I get stuck with the amateurs.
Crap! No one tell MAL about this!
Come on, people! We watched the training videos!
Those were good men. Their names will be forgotten!
You just got knocked the HELL OUT!
Ha-ha! I was like, BOOM, BOOM! DEAD!
Oh, c'mon! I didn't even break a sweat!
We're gonna need more, uh, anything!
We need more people to get shot that aren't me!
Aw, hell yeah, there's my backup!
Nice of you to show up!
Hey new guys! Get to shooting!
I knew corporate would send someone!
Am I glad to see a contractually obligated friendly face!
Bout time you guys showed up!
Welcome to the party! Get shooting!
You can't run from the storm!
That burning sensation means its working!
Can't wait to see your skeleton!
I've got gloves under my gloves!
I can smell this through my suit!
I dare you! I dare you double!
Not easy moving in this thing!
Are you proud of me yet, dad?!
Flames... on the side of your face!
This means I'm big and strong!
Light it up! Shut it down!
You're about to be a hot mess!
Bout to get warm in here!
One of us is gonna love this!
After I crush you, I'm gonna get a fro-gurt!
You can't fence me in! But I can!
Hope you didn't need your shield!
That is some weak sauce right there!
Ohhh-ho-ho-ho! Down for the count! Yeahh!
No-no-no, go ahead. Take your time dyin'! I ain't goin' nowhere! [laughs]
Just taking a little stroll, waiting for you to bleed out! [laughs]
You should see the look on your face! [laughs] You look ridiculous!
That's what you get when you mess with us! [laughs] BOOM!
You! Got taken out! By US! Oh hell yeah!
